nano .gitignore
```

Paste this:
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/
frontend/node_modules/
solana-contract/node_modules/

# Build outputs
frontend/.next/
solana-contract/target/
solana-contract/.anchor/

# Environment files (contains secrets)
frontend/.env.local
.env.local
.env

# Solana keypairs (NEVER push these)
*.json.bak
id.json

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
